---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="bg-[#F5F8FD] py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#004ADD] font-semibold mb-4">Explore & Connect</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-[#02275A] leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em]">
          Activities &amp; Travel
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Discover meaningful experiences beyond the classroom with OLLI at Hampton University. Our activities and travel opportunities bring members together through exploration, connection, and shared interests. From local adventures and cultural experiences to special events and unforgettable journeys, OLLI provides opportunities to stay engaged, build friendships, and continue learning in exciting new ways.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#02275A]">Activities</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
          <p>
            Experience the joy of lifelong learning with OLLI at Hampton University through a wide variety of engaging activities designed to inspire curiosity, creativity, and connection. From educational programs and social gatherings to hands-on experiences and community events, our activities provide opportunities to explore interests, meet new people, and enjoy meaningful experiences with fellow members.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether your interests include arts, history, wellness, technology, culture, or simply spending time with a vibrant community of learners, OLLI activities offer a welcoming environment where members can discover new passions and continue growing at every stage of life.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 rounded-[32px] border-2 border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-[#F8FAFC] p-12 text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-sm">
          <div class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm mx-auto">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-[#004ADD]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m2.25 15.75 5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5 1.409-1.41a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3.182 0l2.909 2.91m-18 3.75h16.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5V6a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5-1.5H3.75A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2.25 6v12a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5Zm10.5-11.25h.008v.008h-.008V8.25Zm.375 0a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-[#02275A]">Activity Gallery</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Photos from OLLI events, gatherings, and member experiences will appear here.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-[#F8FAFC] py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#02275A]">Upcoming Trips</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
          <p>
            OLLI travel opportunities extend the learning experience beyond the classroom, allowing members to explore new places, cultures, and perspectives while building connections with fellow travelers. These journeys complement the conversations and discoveries that begin in our courses, lectures, and special interest groups.
          </p>
          <p>
            From international destinations such as Italy, Costa Rica, London, and Paris to local explorations throughout Hampton Roads and beyond, OLLI trips offer enriching experiences that combine learning, adventure, and fellowship.
          </p>
          <p>
            Future travel opportunities will include a variety of experiences, from longer immersive journeys within the United States and abroad to shorter excursions designed to highlight local history, culture, and attractions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 rounded-[32px] border-2 border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-white p-12 text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-sm">
          <div class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#F5F8FD] shadow-sm mx-auto">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-[#004ADD]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12.75 3.03v.568c0 .334.148.65.405.864l1.068.89c.442.369.535 1.01.216 1.49l-.51.766a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.161.886l-.143.048a1.069 1.069 0 0 0-.673 1.236l.015.064a1.069 1.069 0 0 0 1.014.791.998.998 0 0 1 .727.353l.517.581c.284.32.719.456 1.13.345l246-90.852a1.069 1.069 0 0 0 .531-1.635l-.875-1.051a.998.998 0 0 0-.727-.354 1.069 1.069 0 0 1-1.014-.791l-.015-.064a1.069 1.069 0 0 1 .673-1.235l.143-.049a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.161-.886l.51-.766c.319-.48.226-1.121-.216-1.49l-1.068-.89a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-.405-.864v-.568a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-2.25 0v.568c0 .334-.148.65-.405.864l-1.068.89c-.442.369-.535 1.01-.216 1.49l.51.766a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.161.886l.143.048a1.069 1.069 0 0 1 .673 1.236l-.015.064a1.069 1.069 0 0 1-1.014.791.998.998 0 0 0-.727.353l-.517.581c-.284.32-.719.456-1.13.345l-246-90.852a1.069 1.069 0 0 0-.531 1.635l.875 1.051a.998.998 0 0 0 .727.354 1.069 1.069 0 0 1 1.014.791l.015.064a1.069 1.069 0 0 1-.673 1.235l-.143.049a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.161.886l-.51.766c-.319.48-.226 1.121.216 1.49l1.068.89c.258.215.405.53.405.864v.568a1.125 1.125 0 0 0 2.25 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-[#02275A]">Travel Gallery</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Photos and highlights from past and upcoming OLLI trips will appear here.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#02275A]">Event Vendors</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
          <p>
            Our event vendors help bring OLLI experiences to life by providing quality services, resources, and memorable experiences for our members and community events. From specialty offerings and local partnerships to event support and unique experiences, our vendors contribute to creating engaging and enjoyable gatherings.
          </p>
          <p>
            We value the relationships we build with trusted partners who share our commitment to providing exceptional experiences for the OLLI community.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 rounded-[32px] border-2 border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-[#F8FAFC] p-12 text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-sm">
          <div class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm mx-auto">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-[#004ADD]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 21v-7.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h3a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75V21m-4.5 0H2.36m11.14 0H18m0 0h3.64m-1.39 0V9.349M3.75 21V9.349m0 0a3.001 3.001 0 0 0 3.75-.615A2.993 2.993 0 0 0 9.75 9.75c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.016a2.993 2.993 0 0 0 2.25 1.016c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.015a3.001 3.001 0 0 0 3.75.614m-16.5 0a3.004 3.004 0 0 1-.621-4.72l-.004-.004 6.172-6.166A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 10.607 2h2.419a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 1.525.58l.009.008 6.172 6.166a3.001 3.001 0 0 1-.621 4.72M6.75 18h3.75a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75V13.5a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75H6.75a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v3.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-[#02275A]">Vendor Showcase</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Logos and information about OLLI's trusted event partners will appear here.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
